data.title: 160305-0046 - Tsuyoshi Inukai
data.meta_description:
Japanese politician Tsuyoshi Inukai (犬養 毅, 1855–1932) after being elected president of the Rikken Seiyukai party in 1929 (Showa 4).

Inukai served as cabinet minister and Prime Minister of Japan from 1931 (Showa 6) to his assassination in 1932.
